- Accounts payable (unpaid purchases)
- Unpaid expenses
- Any other obligations that represent debt or future payments

Looking at the initial entries (dated 2023-12-31), I don't see any explicit liability entries. This suggests that the initial liabilities might be zero.

- Purchases with "Unpaid" status
- Any other obligations marked as unpaid

I don't see any purchases marked as "Unpaid" in the payment/receipt_status column. All purchases are marked as "Paid".
